    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>We use Paula Wolfert&#39;s oven recipe. Super simple &#8212; 2 cups of polenta to 8-10 cups of water in a buttered or oiled baking dish, stir to combine. Cook for 1 hour and 20 minutes, stir, cook another 10 minutes, and remove from the oven. Ta-da!</p>
<p>Glad everyone is enjoying their polenta!</p>
