      <p>The polenta recipe sounds delicious!</p>
<p>However, I too am concerned by the use of plastic wrap, especially since it is used to seal in the moisture. Condensation forming on plastic will drip back into the pan, so I don&#39;t think it needs to touch the food to be a problem.</p>
