    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>All this fretting about polenta is such nonsense!  It&#39;s easy&#8230; heavy bottomed pot, gentle heat, stir very occasionally, no worries.  Have made it tons, never hovered and it&#39;s always turned out great. Don&#39;t know how polenta became such a fraught exercise.  Relax and enjoy.  PS I&#39;ve lived in Italy and no one there becomes so paranoid about their polenta. ðŸ™‚</p>
