    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My husband loved baked grits(baby polenta), and I never quite liked the texture of grits.  So I make the corn mush according to the directions, add some butter, egg and milk mixture,seasonings and cheese.  Bake in oven until everything is bubbly.  It&#39;s a great casserole to serve with morning guests or brunch.</p>
