    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2010/03/a-reasonable-question/#comment-17911"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-03-07T04:55:32-05:00">Thursday, March 7, 2013 at 4:55 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I start my polenta the usual way. Once it has thickened a bit, I finish the cooking (45-60 min) in the top of a double boiler, over low-medium heat. Once it&#39;s done, I add butter and parm. It will keep over low heat for a long time.</p>
    </div>

